1 Sequence

2 Methodology

2.1 Prediction Model

Using simple OLS.
Note however that this might lead to indigenous, so better to use Instrumental variables. \[ y_{brt}=\sum_{\{I|I=b,r,d\}}^i{w_ix_i} + \epsilon_{brt} \\ y:Taste, \space b:Beans,\space r:Roasting, \space t:Time, \space d:Dripping, \space \epsilon:Error \]

2.2 Classification Model

Using Principal Component Analysis (PCA).
Plot the results and check also the indigenous between variables especially with roastings and beans.
